'''通播集团'''（{{Lang-en|Comcast Corporation}}），曾用名“康卡斯特控股公司（{{lang|en|Comcast Holdings}}）{{efn|1=在2001年与[[美国电报电话公司|美国电报电话公司]]合并之前，母公司名为“康卡斯特控股公司”。而现在“康卡斯特控股公司”是“通播集团”的子公司，而不再作为母公司存在。<sup>（参见[[彭博社|彭博社]]上[http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=7675764 有关康卡斯特控股公司的资料]）</sup> 从技术上来讲，目前的母公司当初名为“CAB控股公司”，而在改名为“通播集团”之前曾用名“美国电报电话－康卡斯特集团”。<sup>（参见[http://apps.shareholder.com/sec/viewerContent.aspx?companyid=CMCSA&docid=2086089 2002年11月8K/A报表]和[http://www.cmcsa.com/secfiling.cfm?filingID=950103-02-1156 2002年11月S-4文件]）</sup>}}”，是一家位于[[美国|美国]]的全球[[电信|通讯业]][[综合企业|综合企业]]集团；通过{{Link-en|Xfinity|Xfinity}}品牌，其收入在全球[[电信|电信]]及[[有线电视|有线电视]]市场均位居第一。<ref name="mediadb.eu"/> 通播集团同时是美国第二大[[付费电视|付费电视]]服务商；第一大有线电视和家庭[[ISP|互联网接入服务商]]，以及第三大家庭[[电讯公司|电话服务商]]。康卡斯特集团在全美40个州和[[哥伦比亚特区|哥伦比亚特区]]提供商业服务。<ref name="annual_report">[http://files.shareholder.com/downloads/CMCSA/845254023x0xS1193125%2D09%2D33975/1166691/filing.pdf Comcast 2008 Form 10-K] {{Wayback|url=http://files.shareholder.com/downloads/CMCSA/845254023x0xS1193125%2D09%2D33975/1166691/filing.pdf |date=20170421095409 }}, files.shareholder.com</ref> 康卡斯特集团的总部位于美国[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]的[[费城|费城]]。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/companies/comcast/|title=Comcast on the Forbes Global 2000 List|work=Forbes|access-date=2017-06-15|language=en|archive-date=2018-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618183631/https://www.forbes.com/companies/comcast/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 自从2011年开始成为国际传媒集团[[NBC环球|NBC环球集团]]的所有者，<ref name="Comcast-Jan-2011-8-K">{{cite web
  | url        = http://edgar.secdatabase.com/241/95010311000353/filing-main.htm
  | title        = Comcast, Form 8-K, Current Report, Filing Date Jan 31, 2011
  | publisher        = secdatabase.com
  | accessdate        = 2013-03-27
  | archive-date        = 2016-11-07
  | archive-url        = https://web.archive.org/web/20161107130831/http://edgar.secdatabase.com/241/95010311000353/filing-main.htm
  | dead-url        = yes
  }}</ref><ref name="Comcast-Feb-2013-8-K">{{cite web
  | url        = http://pdf.secdatabase.com/571/0000950103-13-001016.pdf
  | title        = Comcast, Form 8-K, Current Report, Filing Date Feb 12, 2013
  | publisher        = secdatabase.com
  | accessdate        = 2013-03-27
  | archive-date        = 2016-11-07
  | archive-url        = https://web.archive.org/web/20161107115818/http://pdf.secdatabase.com/571/0000950103-13-001016.pdf
  | dead-url        = yes
  }}</ref><ref name="Comcast-Mar-2013-8-K">{{cite web
  | url        = http://edgar.secdatabase.com/1408/95010313001853/filing-main.htm
  | title        = Comcast, Form 8-K, Current Report, Filing Date Mar 19, 2013
  | publisher        = secdatabase.com
  | accessdate        = 2013-03-27
  | archive-date        = 2013-05-21
  | archive-url        = https://web.archive.org/web/20130521031312/http://edgar.secdatabase.com/1408/95010313001853/filing-main.htm
  | dead-url        = yes
  }}</ref><ref name="CMCSA-GE Final">(2013-03-19) [http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/comcast-completes-acquisition-nbcuniversal/] {{Wayback|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/03/comcast-completes-acquisition-nbcuniversal/ |date=20140707154122 }}. Deadline, "Comcast Completes Acquisition Of GE’s 49% Stake In NBCUniversal". Retrieved on 2013-03-19.</ref> 康卡斯特集团也成为[[院线|院线]]、[[地面电视|无线电视]]、[[有线电视|有线电视]]等渠道的[[电影|电影]]与[[电视节目|电视节目]]提供商。

康卡斯特集团拥有并运营{{Link-en|Xfinity|Xfinity}}电讯和有线电视服务；全美[[地面电视|无线电视]]联播网（全国广播公司和[[Telemundo电视台|世界电视]]）；多个有线电视频道（包括[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]、[[CNBC|CNBC]]、[[USA電視台|USA电视网]]、[[NBCSN|NBCSN]]、[[E!|E!]]等）；电影制片公司（[[环球影业|环球影业]]）以及位于[[好莱坞环球影城|加利福尼亚州洛杉矶]]、[[奥兰多环球影城度假村|佛罗里达州奥兰多]]和[[大阪环球影城|日本大阪]]的[[环球主题乐园及度假村|环球主题乐园及度假村]]。[[新加坡环球影城|新加坡环球影城]]是康卡斯特集团运营的四大环球影城主题公园之一，但其所有权归[[云顶集团|云顶集团]]；而[[北京环球影城|北京环球影城]]等新环球主题乐园和度假村也将在未来兴建或选址。<ref name="Comcast-Feb-2013-10-K">{{cite web
  | url        = http://edgar.secdatabase.com/1713/119312513067658/filing-main.htm
  | title        = Comcast, Form 10-K, Annual Report, Filing Date Feb 21, 2013
  | publisher        = secdatabase.com
  | accessdate        = 2013-03-27
  | archive-date        = 2013-05-21
  | archive-url        = https://web.archive.org/web/20130521013002/http://edgar.secdatabase.com/1713/119312513067658/filing-main.htm
  | dead-url        = no
  }}</ref> 同时，康卡斯特集团在数字发行渠道方面也有诸多控股资产，例如在2006年收购的{{Link-en|平台 (康卡斯特)|thePlatform|平台}}。2014年2月，康卡斯特集团与{{Link-en|时代华纳有线|Time Warner Cable}}达成一项价值452亿美元的股权置换协议。而根据这份协议，康卡斯特集团将最终全资拥有时代华纳有线公司。<ref>[http://www.broadcastcommunications.com/index.php/sid/220086103/scat/3a8a80d6f705f8cc/ht/Comcast-and-Time-Warner-Cable-to-merge-in-452bn-deal Comcast and Time Warner Cable to merge in $45.2bn deal] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20140214125916/http://www.broadcastcommunications.com/index.php/sid/220086103/scat/3a8a80d6f705f8cc/ht/Comcast-and-Time-Warner-Cable-to-merge-in-452bn-deal |date=2014-02-14 }}. ''Broadcast Communications''. Retrieved on 2014-02-14.</ref> 但是到了2015年4月24日，康卡斯特集团终止了该协议。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://arstechnica.com/business/2015/04/comcast-admits-defeat-terminates-time-warner-cable-merger-agreement/|title=Comcast admits defeat, terminates Time Warner Cable merger agreement|work=Ars Technica|access-date=2017-06-30|language=en-us|archive-date=2017-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170607212632/https://arstechnica.com/business/2015/04/comcast-admits-defeat-terminates-time-warner-cable-merger-agreement/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://corporate.comcast.com/news-information/news-feed/comcast-twc-charter-transactions-terminated|title=Comcast / Time Warner Cable / Charter Transactions Terminated|website=corporate.comcast.com|language=en|access-date=2017-06-30|archive-date=2017-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709082329/http://corporate.comcast.com/news-information/news-feed/comcast-twc-charter-transactions-terminated|dead-url=no}}</ref> 康卡斯特集团在2017年6月与特许通信（{{lang|en|Charter Communications}}）达成协议，将在晚些的时候就收购斯普林特进行独家谈判。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/gadfly/articles/2017-06-27/sprint-shows-desperation-in-sudden-talks-with-cable-guys|title=Sprint's Saviors?|date=2017-06-27|publisher=|via=www.bloomberg.com|access-date=2018-04-24|archive-date=2017-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223041402/https://www.bloomberg.com/gadfly/articles/2017-06-27/sprint-shows-desperation-in-sudden-talks-with-cable-guys|dead-url=no}}</ref>

康卡斯特集团因为多种理由而备受批评；其有线电视服务的客户满意度位居业界后列。<ref>{{cite web
 |url          = http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/comcast-is-crowned-consumeristcoms-2010-worst-company-in-america-92097574.html
 |title        = Comcast Is Crowned Consumerist.Com's 2010 'Worst Company in America'
 |publisher    = PR Newswire
 |author       = Consumerist
 |date         = 2010-04-26
 |accessdate   = 2014-03-31
 |archive-date = 2021-02-16
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20210216230352/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/comcast-is-crowned-consumeristcoms-2010-worst-company-in-america-92097574.html
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref><ref name="JDP-score">[http://news.ecoustics.com/bbs/messages/10381/518826.html J.D. Power Releases 2008 Residential Television Service Satisfaction Survey] {{Wayback|url=http://news.ecoustics.com/bbs/messages/10381/518826.html |date=20091005025055 }}. News.ecoustics.com. Retrieved on 2011-07-08.</ref> 此外，康卡斯特集团过去曾违反[[网络中立性|网络中立性]]原则；尽管康卡斯特集团承诺恪守网络中立性的狭义定义，<ref name=Netflix>{{cite web
 |url          = http://www.cnet.com/news/netflixs-hastings-makes-the-case-for-net-neutrality/
 |title        = Netflix's Hastings makes the case for Net neutrality
 |publisher    = Cnet
 |author       = Dara Kerr
 |date         = 2014-03-20
 |accessdate   = 2014-03-31
 |archive-date = 2021-02-01
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20210201031543/https://www.cnet.com/news/netflixs-hastings-makes-the-case-for-net-neutrality/
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref> 但是批评人士指出这个定义无视了康卡斯特[[专用网络|专用网络]]服务与康卡斯特其他网络接入服务之间的差别。<ref name="FCC-VOIP">Modine, Austin. (2009-01-21) [https://www.theregister.co.uk/2009/01/21/fcc_letter_comcast_voip_traffic_management/ TheRegister.co.uk] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2009/01/21/fcc_letter_comcast_voip_traffic_management/ |date=20190611131302 }}. TheRegister.co.uk. Retrieved on 2011-07-08.</ref> 同时批评人士也指责康卡斯特的绝大多数服务地区缺乏竞争，有线电视服务商之间的竞争有限。<ref>{{cite news
 |url          = http://articles.latimes.com/2013/aug/23/business/la-fi-hiltzik-20130823
 |title        = Cable monopolies hurt consumers and the nation
 |website      = Los Angeles Times
 |author       = Michael Hiltzik
 |date         = 2013-08-23
 |accessdate   = 2014-03-31
 |archive-date = 2014-04-02
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20140402063038/http://articles.latimes.com/2013/aug/23/business/la-fi-hiltzik-20130823
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref> 此外还考虑到康卡斯特集团作为[[ISP|互联网接入服务商]]巨头的谈判能力，康卡斯特集团极可能利用付费对等原则来不公平地影响[[终端用户|终端用户]]的互联网接入速度。同时由于康卡斯特同时拥有内容的制作能力和分发能力，这也引发了业界有关“[[垄断|垄断]]”的担忧。这些以及其他问题导致康卡斯特集团在2010年和2014年两度成为消费者票选出来的“全美最差公司”。<ref>{{cite news
 |url          = http://consumerist.com/2014/04/08/congratulations-to-comcast-your-2014-worst-company-in-america/
 |title        = Congratulations To Comcast, Your 2014 Worst Company In America!
