 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>

康卡斯特集团同时还在州政府级别进行游说和组建政治行动委员会，例如其对田纳西州有线电信协会<small>（{{lang|en|Tennessee Cable Telecommunications Association}}）</small>和华盛顿州宽带通讯协会<small>（{{lang|en|Broadband Communications Association of Washington}}）</small>的政治行动委员会的支持。<ref>{{cite web
 |url          = http://www.timesfreepress.com/news/2011/may/30/lobbyists-had-busy-year-nashville/
 |title        = Lobbyists had busy year in Nashville
 |publisher    = Times Free Press
 |author       = Andy Sher
